  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nWhy does solidity treat variable name and function name shadowing differently?\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  {\r\n    // Okay: Shadows namesake variable in outer scope\r\n    let x := 2\r\n  }\r\n  let x := 1\r\n  // Okay: Stores 1 at address 0\r\n  mstore(0, x);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  {\r\n    // Not Okay: Shadows namesake function in outer scope\r\n    function foo() {}\r\n  }\r\n  function foo() {}\r\n}\r\n```",
